{"tid":751884,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[平民廚房](有片)(圖文) 鹽焗魚 配 番茄沙沙","createTime":"2018-07-22T09:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T12:25:01.000Z","uid":156466,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7f961208ddc577c9fbb1d822a3df12c010db87","tid":751884,"uid":156466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6HI5uNOUa18&amp;t=7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6HI5uNOUa18%26t%3D7s&d=jM4Xazfkj6lOjvklLJQOxQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=73ebcfcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6HI5uNOUa18&amp;t=7s</a><br />\n<br />\n我會繼續出片 今次同大家講下鹽焗魚 <br />\n材料同造法都簡單 係屋企有焗爐就做到 係D鹽要買多少少姐<br />\n再整埋個番茄沙沙去跟條魚一齊食 拍完片冇幾分鐘條魚就俾我地食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下大家 如果 我話如果<br />\n如果有返咁上下人睇 到時我搞個抽獎遊戲仔請大家食野<br />\n你地覺得咁玩好唔好?<br />\n戴個頭盔 不過我唔知連登俾唔俾咁玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過都就執 就算想再請落去都唔知幾時先可以再請</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/172229_b5f8740efaa795fbe7a4d99d6e6c4b50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F172229_b5f8740efaa795fbe7a4d99d6e6c4b50.jpg&h=c32c08fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171448_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171448_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=050e3f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n材料如下:<br />\n- 魚 1斤起 免打鱗<br />\n- 粗鹽 約5斤以上<br />\n- 蒜頭5瓣<br />\n- 刁草 1束<br />\n- 檸檬 2個<br />\n<br />\n番茄沙沙:<br />\n- 番茄半個 切碎粒<br />\n- 紫洋蔥／乾蔥 切碎粒<br />\n- 番茜／羅勒 少許 切碎<br />\n- 初榨欖油 少許<br />\n- 辣椒乾碎<br />\n- 黑椒 少許<br />\n- 檸檬汁 少許<br />\n<br />\n20 &deg;C入焗爐焗15-18分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171507_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171507_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=10065170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171507_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171507_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=776ed2b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.\t落蛋白落鹽到係為左等佢焗既時候D鹽唔會散開哂<br />\n倒哂D鹽落個mixing bowl到  續隻蛋白落落去<br />\n搓勻佢  如果你揸下佢發現唔可以揸成一團野  就再繼續落蛋白繼續搓<br />\n直到佢可以揸做一團野而唔會散開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171527_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171527_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=462a8871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.\t洗魚  係條魚到開一刀  撩哂佢D內臟啊 血啊出黎 洗乾淨佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171537_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171537_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=f8858911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171538_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171538_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=312a6870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.\t用毛巾或廚紙內內外外咁印乾佢 最緊要印乾 唔好有水殘留 咁樣條魚雪係雪櫃都keep得耐 同埋無咁腥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171556_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171556_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg&h=19243593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.\t壓一壓D蒜頭 塞哂入條魚入面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171557_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171557_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg&h=9d15ab99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5.\t再塞哂D Dill草入去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171557_30e62fddc14c05988b44e7c02788e187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171557_30e62fddc14c05988b44e7c02788e187.jpg&h=995a7351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6.\t用檸檬片封住個魚肚 除左有D檸檬味之外 等焗既時候D鹽唔會走入去 如果唔係條魚就會太鹹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171649_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171649_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg&h=26c0f409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171708_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171708_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg&h=e3ad2c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7.\t拎個焗盤出黎鋪張牛油紙先<br />\n8.\t首先就將頭先撈好左既鹽鋪一層做底  再放條魚上去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171722_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171722_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg&h=676e8b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9.\t再續D續D咁鋪埋D鹽上條魚 包實佢 魚頭同魚尾露出黎都OK 唔重要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171746_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171746_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg&h=c97c7bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10.\t隊佢入焗爐 衣條魚1斤鬆D 我地200&deg;C焗佢15~18分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171841_edab7ba7e203cd7576d1200465194ea8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171841_edab7ba7e203cd7576d1200465194ea8.jpg&h=5db81314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171841_db3a17f7bcac837ecc1fe2bc630a5473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171841_db3a17f7bcac837ecc1fe2bc630a5473.jpg&h=f1a0e126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11.\t係焗既時候可以整埋個番茄沙沙<br />\n番茄紫洋蔥parsley切粒切碎 連埋D辣椒乾碎倒哂入個兜仔 <br />\n落D欖油落D鹽糖<br />\n再落D pepper同檸檬汁 撈下佢<br />\n落幾多好隨意既 食落有D酸有D辣甜甜地咁好開胃就OK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171858_85b6f89b41cae26786ac72365fff771b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171858_85b6f89b41cae26786ac72365fff771b.jpg&h=5fad9247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171858_64b8299d1597b8a5c7b9cb9c88642f6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171858_64b8299d1597b8a5c7b9cb9c88642f6c.jpg&h=700197ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12.\t焗完拎條魚出黎 連牛油紙搬過去一隻大碟到 再將邊邊的牛油紙撕走佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171910_a269962fe1424e1ca3e68c328b9fed61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171910_a269962fe1424e1ca3e68c328b9fed61.jpg&h=82c62f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n13.\t搵碌野敲下D鹽 敲散佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/171921_e89666feb714ab9c3946f28f00c5d8c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F171921_e89666feb714ab9c3946f28f00c5d8c4.jpg&h=61002b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14.\t拎走蓋住條魚D鹽 露哂條魚出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/172057_ca538c343179bf0fbdfab6cd10469afd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F172057_ca538c343179bf0fbdfab6cd10469afd.jpg&h=44c2e409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/172058_030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F172058_030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f4.jpg&h=7a974619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n15.\t將條魚個肚裡面D野拎出黎 放係碟邊 等人食既時候知道你落左咁多料<br />\n再用刀仔緣住魚邊cut塊魚皮 慢慢起哂成塊魚皮 露D魚肉出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/172147_134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F172147_134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b723.jpg&h=ef6d655f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/172147_648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F172147_648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec.jpg&h=68264bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n16.   落D pepper 落D欖油係面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/172155_adaf0ad2e085c835a82b2f021fe236ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F172155_adaf0ad2e085c835a82b2f021fe236ae.jpg&h=708c9a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/172156_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F172156_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg&h=2cde8ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n17.   Fucking done."},{"pid":"e35f3fcf13a96c0